Cape Town - A video has been making the rounds and scaring people on social media.The video was posted to Facebook by Jason Womal, a tradesman from Coppabella in Queensland, Australia.Womal explained that as he was about to head out for work when his neighbour called him over, offering to show him something cool.&#x201C;So we proceed to his place and he shows me this,&quot; Womal writes on Facebook. &quot;Huntsman trying to eat a mouse.&#x201D;The video depicts the giant spider clutching a mouse by its head with its chelicerae while it crawls up the refrigerator.A voice can be heard off screen wondering, &#x201C;What&#x2019;s he gonna do with him? Man that is so cool&#x201D;. IOL IOL News on Facebook IOL on Twitter